reviews.text: a friendly and tasty local restaurant!

Hopefully, this message will be read by the owner. I visited your restaurant once/twice a year. This is my 11th visit. In these last two years, you roasted goose quality dropped significantly. Last year, I went to your place in the evening and found the goose was soft and chewy. The bamboo soup was sold out. Then, I revisited on the next day and found both dishes desirable. However, two days ago I went to your restaurant at 11 am because I was afraid that the roasted goose would sit too long. I found the goose was very chewy, cold and disappointing. I used to be a fan of your place. I'm reconsidering if I should go back to your place.
Always satisfied with good valued food and friendly old Chinese waiters
Very great place! I have been here twice in one day.

reviews.text: 숙소 앞 아무생각없이 해장하러 들어간 곳. 가금류의 로스트 미트가 주력 메뉴인듯 했으나 막상 들어가보니 현지 사람들이 전부 인스턴트 누들을 먹고 있음. 아침이라서 더 그랬던 것 같기도 하고. 해장이 목적이었으니 인스턴트 누들과 로스트포크 덮밥 같은 메뉴를 시킴. 무난무난 했고 영어 메뉴판은 있으나 점원 아주머니들과 의사소통은 전혀 되지 않았음. 인스턴트 누들은 대체적으로 담백한 맛의 메뉴들이 많고 얼큰하거나 매운 종류의 것은 없는듯 하다.
a friendly and tasty local restaurant!

reviews.text: Roast meat is delicious, whether it is a barbecued pork, oyster chicken or roast duck. This restaurant offers meals to customers throughout the day. A set lunch consists of a soup, main course, rice and drinks for about HK$80.
Had vegetarian options with symbols in the menu to represent them. English menu was a big help. Food was not bad, good for a late night meal when no else vegetarian place is open.
Good basic food reasonably priced
Just a regular Cantonese restaurant, nothing special, the goose was not cooked very well

Rude service, unhygienic (they forced us to sit next to a table with a dirty water bucket even though the place was empty and we asked to be seated somewhere else), and filthy cutlery and crockery. We took one look at the menu and then left.
